---
title: Chermoula Beef & Veggie Couscous with Garlic Dip & Flaked Almonds
description: THere's couscous, and then tHere's veggie couscous. The key here is to cook it to fluffy perfection, then take it to another level by bringing it together with fresh elements like capsicum and tomato. It serves as the perfect bed for juicy, spiced beef.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/676d0b81d8e11bf886851681-91adb134-945de772.jpeg
